</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                             B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   And the Lord has shown the designs of His love
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                      Em
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   designs of ineffable art for every man.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                   B7
