</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and terrible cries were heard
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                           B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   like cries of women in labor.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   C
