</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                   B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. And the designs were lost
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           Am                    B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and the angels of heaven were crying,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   the designs of all those
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                          B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   who did not follow His truth.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   C                           B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Because the Lord showed His way
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and He showered His grace
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   upon all those who follow Him;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   C
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and gave them the strength
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                               B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   to grow beautiful with His holiness.

